Antennae 0.9× head length. Ant. I, II and III with 5, 9−10 and 15 ordinary chaetae, respectively. AIIIO consist- ing of two small rounded internal sensory rods and two short guard sensilla, the external sensillum backward displaced; with ventral microsensillum present (
